<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Curse of Weakness (W)</b></li><ul><li> The initial base damage of this ability has been reduced to 30/45/60/75/90, down from 30/55/80/105/130.</li></ul><li><b>Devour (E)</b></li><ul><li> The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 55/95/135/175/215, down from 55/100/145/190/235.</li></ul><li><b>Damnation(R)</b></li><ul><li> The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 175/300/425, down from 200/325/450.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Sentinel Strike (Q)</b></li><ul><li> Fixed a bug where activating this ability would reset Voluc's basic attack cooldown but not cleave correctly.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 35 (September 11, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Curse of Weakness (W)</b></li><ul><li> The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 30/55/80/105/130, down from 35/60/85/110/135.</li></ul><li><b>Damnation (R)</b></li><ul><li> The based damage of this ability has been reduced to 200/325/450, down from 200/350/500.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 34 (August 19th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Mark of Consumption (Passive)</b></li><ul><li>Voluc will now only heal for 50% of the damage dealt by this passive, down from 100%.</li></ul><li><b>Sentinel Strike (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 40/75/110/145/180, down from 50/85/120/155/190.</li><li>The cooldown reduction component of this ability versus non-Shaper enemies has been removed.</li></ul><li><b>Devour (E)</b></li><ul><li>The Haste granted by this ability per target struck has been reduced to 5/7.5/10/12.5/15, down from 9/13/17/21/25.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 33 (July 29th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Voluc now has a passive:</li><ul><li><b>Mark of Consumption - </b>Whenever Voluc deals damage with an ability to a target he applies a Mark of Consumption, causing them to take 3% (+1.5% per 100 Power) of their maximum health as magical damage over 2 seconds. Voluc is healed an amount equal to the damage dealt. Damage against non-Shaper is reduced to 1.5% (+0.75% per 100 Power) of their maximum Health.</li></ul><li><b>Sentinel Strike (Q)</b></li><ul><li>Basic attacks against non-Shapers now reduce the cooldown of this ability by 0.25 seconds, down from 0.33 seconds.</li></ul><li><b>Curse of Weakness (W)</b></li><ul><li>The passive Lifedrain granted by this ability has been removed.</li></ul><li><b>Devour (E)</b></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 55/100/145/190/235, down from 60/105/150/195/240.</li></ul><li><b>Damnation (R)</b></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been adjusted to 200/350/500 over 4 seconds, from 280/360/440.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Base Stats</b></li><ul><li>Base Health has been reduced to 525, down from 540.</li><li>Base health per level has been reduced to 78, down from 84.</li></ul><li><b>Curse of Weakness (W)</b></li><ul><li>The initial damage of this ability has been reduced to 35/60/85/110/135, down from 35/65/95/125/155.</li><li>The damage dealt by this ability upon triggering the mark has been reduced to 50/75/100/125/150, down from 55/85/115/145/175.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where this ability would sometimes fail to reset Voluc's basic attack cooldown.</li><li>Fixed a bug where this ability would sometimes cause an overlay animation error where he would display an improper animation during the basic attack.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Devour (E)</B></li><ul><li>This ability now has a 0.15 second cast time.</li><li>The damage of this ability has been reduced to 50/105/150/195/240, down from 65/110/155/200/245.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The damage of this ability has been reduced to 50/85/120/155/190, down from 60/95/130/165/200.</li></ul><li><b>Curse of Weakness (W)</b></li><ul><li>The initial base damage of this ability has been reduced to 35/65/95/125/155, down from 40/70/100/130/160.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been changed to 60/95/130/165/200, from 55/95/135/175/215.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.7, down from 0.8.</li></ul><li><B>Curse of Weakness (W)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the debuff visual effect would sometimes fail to display on the affected target.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Curse of Weakness (W)</li><ul><li>The base damage dealt by damaging an enemy marked with this ability has been reduced to 55/85/115/145/175, down from 55/90/125/160/195.</li></ul><li>Damnation (R)</li><ul><li>The passive Lifedrain percentage granted by this ability has been reduced to 25/50/75%, down from 50/75/100%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Sentinel Strike (Q)</li><ul><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.8, down from 1.2.</li></ul><li>Curse of Weakness (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 575, from previous value of 625.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.3, down from 0.4.</li><li>The Power ratio of the mark triggered upon basic damaging a marked enemy has been reduced to 0.5, down from 0.7.</li></ul><li>Devour (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 540, from previous value of 600.</li></ul><li>Damnation (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 400, from previous value of 450.</li><li>The Power ratio for this ability has been reduced to 1.0, down from 1.2.</li><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 100/90/80, down from 120/110/100.</li><li>This ability no longer heals Voluc for the amount of damage it deals. Instead, Voluc will now be granted 50/75/100% bonus Lifedrain for the duration.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 13 (October 13, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Curse of Weakness (W)</B></li><ul><li>The damage this ability inflicts when Voluc triggers the marked target has been reduced to 55/90/125/160/195, down from 65/100/135/170/205.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 8 (August 09, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cleave component of this ability now no longer grants an additional 40 range to Voluc's basic attack.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 7 (August 02, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Basic attack range increased to 170, up from 130.</li><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B></li><ul><li>This ability will now have it's cooldown reduced by 0.33 seconds per basic attack against non-shapers, in addition to it's reduction of 2 seconds per basic attack against Shapers.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Cleave damage adjusted to 55/95/135/175/215 from 70/105/140/175/210. Sentinel Strike will now have it's cooldown decreased by 2 seconds when Voluc hits an enemy Shaper with a basic attack, up from a 1 second decrease in cooldown.</li></ul><li><B>Curse of Weakness (W)</B></li><ul><li>The projectile speed on Curse of Weakness has been increased by 50%. The major slow on Curse of Weakness has been increased to 40/45/50/55/60%, up from 35/40/45/50/55%. The duration of the minor slow of Curse of Weakness has been increased to 4 seconds, up from 3 seconds. The duration of the minor slow component of Curse of Weakness has been increased to 2 seconds, up from 1.5 seconds.</li></ul><li><B>Devour (E)</B></li><ul><li>Area of effect damage adjusted to 65/110/155/200/245 from 75/115/155/195/235.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 1 (June 06, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Sentinel Strike (Q)</B><ul><li>Activating Sentinel Strike while auto-attacking before the hit connects will now instantly reset Voluc's auto attack animation and cause his next strike to cleave. We have also fixed a bug where Sentinel Strike was not receiving increased base damage at higher ranks.</li></ul></li><li><B>Curse of Weakness (W)</B><ul><li>Fixed a bug where Curse of Weakness was not receiving increased base damage at higher ranks.<BR><BR><I>Developer Notes - We felt that Voluc's jungle clear speed was a bit too fast. The below changes should bring him in line with other junglers without hurting his teamfighting ability.</I><BR><BR></li></ul><li><B>Devour (E)</B><ul><li>Haste bonus adjusted to 9/13/17/21/25 from 8/13/18/23/28. Additionally, the haste bonus now only stacks 4 times, down from 5. This results in the maximum haste received from the ability to be adjusted to 36/52/68/84/100, down from 40/65/90/115/140.</li></ul></li></ul>